        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "."
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "Bristol is one of the great low-volume British luxury makes, combining style and performance in a way few can. Back in the 1950s, they went into business with a Chicagoan named Stephen \"Wacky\" Arnolt to "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "build sports racers"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " in a factory in Warsaw, Indiana."
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      10,
      1
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "These two-seat roadsters"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " were powered by Bristol's 2.0 liter inline six cylinder, originally designed by BMW and claimed by the British after World War II. The whole package is wrapped up in a beautiful, swoopy body penned by Bertone."
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "So, is it British, American, German, or Italian? The "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "correct answer"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " is a simple \"yes.\""
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      10,
      2
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "The car seen here"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " is one of just 142 produced in the five-year period between 1954 and 1959. It was, miraculously, restored in roughly 100 days after spending half a century languishing in a garage. It was completed just in time to make its debut at the Pebble Beach Concours dâ€™Elegance. "
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "Restoring any car in 100 days is impressive, but to restore "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "an exceedingly rare car"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " like this and immediately show it off at the most prestigious concours show in the world is quite an accomplishment."
        ]
      ]
    ],
